---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Contact - Insight Hunter">
  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Contact Information</p>
    <p>Reach out to Insight Hunter for support, inquiries, or partnerships. Our team is available to assist with product questions, technical issues, or custom solutions.</p>
    <p>Email: support@insighthunter.app | Phone: +1-123-456-7890 | Address: 123 Finance St, Atlanta, GA 30301</p>
    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/yourformid" method="POST"> <!-- Replace 'yourformid' with actual Formspree ID -->
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
      <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" rows="6" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
    </form>
    <p>For FAQs, visit the dedicated page. Company updates in updates section. News and tech details available accordingly.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
